version_description:
Welcome to Newburyton!
Christmas is coming, and the town is buzzing with excitement!
There are new wonderful stories to explore, and lots of interesting characters to meet!
We have many challenging and fun events coming soon!
Update the app to merge now!
Merry Christmas!

Breaking News from Newburyton!
The official version has now been released!
There are new wonderful stories to explore, and lots of interesting characters to meet!
There will also be more new events happening around town, so keep a lookout!
Have fun, and keep merging!

Welcome to Newburyton, where there’s something fun happening every day!
There are new events coming, full of unique stories and friendly new characters for you to meet!
Update your game now to enjoy all the fun to be had in Merge County!
You don’t want to miss it!

Welcome to Newburyton!
We’ve always believed that merging makes happiness!
The second season of the Garden Isle event is coming! Ready to have some more merging fun?
Update the game now! Your friends in town are waiting for you!
